{"tid":1070994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭月娥：首兩個月樓價止跌回升   感憂慮","createTime":"2019-03-21T04:50:34.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-21T06:27:33.000Z","uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"80ca415af7a0e6689ede21ff442e84e0cc3d2c12","tid":1070994,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:50:34.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448856-20190321.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448856-20190321.htm&d=01EY%2BZdPKRb21p6QCrTOV%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=6e95bf05\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1448856-20190321.htm&h=e7a01e56\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1448856-20190321.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n行政長官林鄭月娥表示，本港樓價去年8月開始下調約9至10%，不過今年首兩個月，樓價止跌回升，令她感到憂慮，因為負擔能力對市民是重要的事，而本港作為奉行自由經濟的社會，唯一解決方法是增加政府角色和功能。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥出席一個投資論壇時說，政府早前已提出多項措施，包括改變資助房屋定價方式，與市價脫勾；將公私營房屋比例改至七比三；建立置業階梯，包括引入綠置居及港人首置計劃；政府亦全盤接納土地供應專責小組建議，多管齊下地增加土地供應，她呼籲政黨支持維港以外填海建人工島的計劃，增加土地。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭月娥又說，明白如果不有效應對本港的房屋問題，她不會是一個好的特首。"},{"pid":"ab3fc414ff72efca479e39390c9134ef8949547d","tid":1070994,"uid":50386,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:53:50.000Z","msg":"她呼籲政黨支持維港以外填海建人工島的計劃，增加土地。<br />\n<br />\n而家啲人買唔起樓，叫人支持個20年後先有單位落成嘅計劃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"284abf807f546a3dea488f24e5532527bff15e3c","tid":1070994,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T04:59:50.000Z","msg":"你故意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"10cd924470f67c22d6304592c882d90662300f19","tid":1070994,"uid":10692,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:01:49.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3d8159164b3e523c62c728849076f6f9c354e548","tid":1070994,"uid":117729,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:02:23.000Z","msg":"增加土地供應，但又唔會賤賣土地，係咩玩法"},{"pid":"d855fbd1a06f351fe8a046d782f292884cbb9204","tid":1070994,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:02:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"89af24c38b572cd8cb98d1252cc8518d9a58579b","tid":1070994,"uid":130695,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:03:47.000Z","msg":"痴撚線政府"},{"pid":"3d208cc280d252431bd3a304aa3c29338bdf40a9","tid":1070994,"uid":10692,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:04:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b39b7ec615db4c6421e38f76132c7cdbb31a6f0d","tid":1070994,"uid":70786,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T05:27:37.000Z","msg":"想為填海鋪路慳D啦<br />\n講到自己為市民擔憂<br />\n你食刁之祿<br />\n擔刁賓周架咋死臭雞"},{"pid":"4c22bd7fe52df1aef7e0855b1f0575b165c303ce","tid":1070994,"uid":190540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-21T06:27:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}